title: Penny Palabras 01-03 (2013- |Digital-HD|Hollow Scene) [REQ]
description:
Promotional info for the first issue - "Penny Palabras, 17, has experienced the paranormal for years. She knows that things aren't always what they seem. Now, she's tormented by a malevolent entity called the Straw Man. As she searches for ways to banish him from her life, she's haunted by more than ghosts. Her nightmares won't let her sleep, her friends and family can't understand, and the Straw Man is getting more powerful every day."

Thanks to Hollow Scene for these Digital copies, and STFMaryville for initially posting these - I consolidated the .cbr files only, to fill a request from KAT and because the single packs were slow/dead. Please seed, and enjoy! :-)
